revision.text:
The '''Ninth Assembly District of Connecticut''' elects one member of the [[Connecticut House of Representatives]]. Its current representative is Jason Rojas. The district consists of parts of the cities of [[East Hartford, Connecticut|East Hartford]] and  [[Manchester, Connecticut|Manchester]] and parts of the town of [[Glastonbury, Connecticut|Glastonbury]]. 

